ZH: 我需要一套黑色的西装。
EN: I need a black suit.

ZH: 他穿着一套精致的西装去参加晚宴。
EN: He wore an exquisite suit to the banquet.

ZH: 我爸爸工作时总是穿着西装。
EN: My dad always wears a suit to work.

ZH: 她喜欢穿着女士西装出席正式场合。
EN: She likes to wear a women's suit for formal occasions.

ZH: 我准备好了一套新西装以备不时之需。
EN: I have a new suit ready just in case.

