EN: He always wears a suit and tie at business meetings.

ZH: 爷爷喜欢穿着一套老式的西装。
EN: Grandpa likes to wear an old-fashioned suit.

ZH: 她买了一套粉色的西装。
EN: She bought a pink suit.

ZH: 我们都得穿着西装去参加婚礼。
EN: We all have to wear suits to the wedding.

ZH: 这套西装的质量非常好。
EN: The quality of this suit is excellent.

ZH: 他在公司里被称为"西装男士"。
EN: He is known as the "suit man" at the company.

ZH: 她喜欢把西装搭配运动鞋。
EN: She likes to pair suits with sneakers.

