EN: The gray suit suits him well.

ZH: 我宁愿穿着西装打扮得体。
EN: I prefer to dress formally in a suit.

ZH: 老板总是穿着一套高级西装。
EN: The boss always wears a high-end suit.

ZH: 整洁的西装是成功的象征。
EN: A neat suit is a symbol of success.

ZH: 学生们都穿着整齐的西装参加毕业典礼。
EN: The students all wore smart suits to the graduation ceremony.

ZH: 因为热, 他解开了西装的领子。
EN: Because it was hot, he loosened the collar of his suit.
